%% Diagram: Three-color DFS node states for cycle detection
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> White
    White: White\n(unvisited)
    Gray: Gray\n(on current\nDFS path)
    Black: Black\n(fully explored)

    White --> Gray: dfs(node)\nenters
    Gray --> Black: all out-edges\nexplored
    Gray --> Cycle: edge to a Gray\nnode = back edge
    Cycle: Cycle\ndetected
    Cycle --> [*]
    Black --> [*]
